                                        </p>
                                        <small><i class="fa fa-clock-o"></i> 5 mins   31 March 2018</small>
                                    </div>
                                </li>
                                <!-- /.item -->
                                <li class="item">
                                    <div class="product-img">
                                        <img src="~/images/1.jpg" alt="Product Image">
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="product-info">
                                        <a href="#" class="product-title">bdtask Hospital Limited</a>
                                        <p>
                                            It is a long established fact that a reader will be distracted by the readable content of a page when looking at its layout.
                                        </p>
                                        <small><i class="fa fa-clock-o"></i> 5 mins   31 March 2018</small>
                                    </div>
                                </li>
                                <!-- /.item -->
                                <li class="item">
                                    <div class="product-img">
                                        <img src="~/images/1.jpg" alt="Product Image">
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="product-info">
                                        <a href="#" class="product-title">bdtask Hospital Limited</a>
                                        <p>
                                            It is a long established fact that a reader will be distracted by the readable content of a page when looking at its layout.
                                        </p>
                                        <small><i class="fa fa-clock-o"></i> 5 mins   31 March 2018</small>
                                    </div>
                                </li>
                                <!-- /.item -->
                                <!-- /.item -->
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <!-- /.box-body -->
                        <div class="box-footer text-center">
                            <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="uppercase">View All Pharmacy News</a>
                        </div>
                        <!-- /.box-footer -->
                    </div>
                    <!-- /.box -->
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>